# API Rules

- Use Route Handlers (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE exports).
- Validate request bodies with Zod.
- Return NextResponse.json() with proper status codes.
- Check authentication before processing protected routes.

## Endpoints

- `POST` `/api/billing/checkout` [AUTH]
- `POST` `/api/billing/portal` [AUTH]
- `POST` `/api/billing/webhook`
- `GET` `/api/health`
- `GET` `/api/repos` [AUTH]
- `POST` `/api/scan/:repoId` [AUTH]
- `GET` `/api/scan/:repoId/download` [AUTH]
- `GET` `/api/scan/:repoId/latest` [AUTH]
- `GET` `/api/scan/:repoId/stream` [AUTH]
- `GET` `/api/search` [AUTH]
- `POST` `/api/webhooks/github`
